  "promptDailyGuidance": "Rubuta gajeriyar jagoran yau da aka tushe a imani na Sunni — tushe a Qur'ani, Hadisi, da koyarwar Annabi Muhammad. Zaɓi kwatancen sabuwa kowane lokaci: fa'idi ne daga ilimin Islama, gaskiya daga Sunnah, hikimar daga Sahabai ko aiki mai natsuwa daga al'adu na Islama. Samu ayar Qur'ani guda (Surah:Ayah) da tunani mai tsantsan dokoki 1–2 don ransa cikin ranar. Daidai da alwatika danganta shi ne da kalandar Islami ko ranar mahimmaciyya idan ta dace.",

  "promptFaithTrust": "Rubuta gajeriyar tunani kan Imani da tabbatarwa a shirin Allah (Tawakkul). Tushe a Qur'ani, misalin Annabi Muhammad, da imani na Sahabai. Canja jaya-jaya: tabbatarwa a lokacin rashin tabbatarwa, asali ga hikimar Allah, haƙuri a cikin gwaji, ko jikim aiki mai natsuwa. Samu ayar Qur'ani guda da mataki gida ɗaya tunani daga ilimin Islama.",

  "promptPrayerReflection": "Rubuta gajeriyar tunani kan sallah tushe a Salah, Dua, ko Dhikr. Canja nau'in: rani mai safiya ko jiya da alkaramsu (Adhkar), tunani kan sallahi biyar, tunani akan ayar Qur'ani, ko addu'a mai zafi. Samu ayar Qur'ani guda da saurin jiya nau'in sallah da aka yi.",

  "promptHopeDifficultTimes": "Rubuta tunani kan haƙuri da niyya a lokacin wahalar. Ɗauki daga koyarwar Qur'ani game da gwaji, jikim Annabai, da jinni Allah a matakin wahalii. Canja hanya kowane lokaci. Samu ayar Qur'ani guda da hankalin ƙarfi daga al'adu na Islama.",

  "promptForgiveness": "Rubuta hikimar tunani kan neman gafara (Tawbah) da jinni Allah. Ɗauki daga koyarwar Qur'ani game da tawbah, jinni Allah, da misalin gafararren Annabi Muhammad. Canja jaya-jaya: koma ga Allah, gafara wa juna, gyara dangantaka, ko imani a jinni Allah. Samu ayar Qur'ani guda da mataki gida ɗaya.",

  "promptLoveCompassion": "Rubuta gajeriyar tunani kan jinni (Rahmah) da tausayi a rayuwar yau. Ɗauki daga misalin Annabi Muhammad, ra'ayin Ihsan (kyau), da koyarwar Islama game da kirki ga iyali, maƙwabta, da marasa iko. Samu ayar Qur'ani guda da ɓata kirki ɗaya don aiki yau.",

  "promptStrengthCourage": "Rubuta tunani kan karfi tushe a imani da jajire. Ɗauki daga misalan Annabai, jama'ar Musulmi na farko, da masu imani da suka tsaya tunani a wahalar. Canja jaya-jaya: jajire a imani, karfi a sallah, tabbatarwa a lokacin tsoron Allah, ko jikim aiki a wahalii. Samu ayar Qur'ani guda da addu'a ɗam-ɗam ko kalmomi na alkhamar.",

  "promptGratitude": "Rubuta tunani kan godiya (Shukr) ga Allah. Tushe a koyarwar Qur'ani da al'adu annabi. Canja hanya: godiya a wahalii, mutunta bayanai ƙarami, fara rana a yabe Allah, ko gane jagoran Allah a yau-yau. Samu ayar Qur'ani guda da aikin godiya ɗaya.",

  "promptPurposeCalling": "Rubuta tunani kan burin rayuwa a bauta Allah da raina da gaskiya. Ɗauki daga koyarwar Qur'ani game da burin, hidima wa juna, da amfani da kalandar ɗinka don alheri. Canja jaya-jaya: hidima ga iyali da gida, neman jadwalin Allah ta Istikhara, rayuwa mai niyya, ko neman ma'ana a aiki na yau-yau. Samu ayar Qur'ani guda da tambayoyi biyu na tunani.",

  "promptFamilyRelationships": "Rubuta jagoran Islama game da iyali da dangantaka tushe a Qur'ani da misalin Annabi Muhammad. Canja jaya-jaya: kirki a halin iyali, haƙuri a kunya, girmama magajiya, girke da yara a imani, ko jajire aure. Samu ayar Qur'ani guda da aikin dangantaka ɗaya don yunƙuri.",

  "promptPeaceAnxietyRelief": "Rubuta tunani mai natsuwa game da neman zaman lafiya a alkhamar Allah (Dhikr) da tabbatarwa a shirin sa. Ɗauki daga koyarwar Qur'ani game da jiya zafi na zafi, sallah, da bada kai ga burin Allah. Canja hanya kowane lokaci da samu ayar Qur'ani guda da aikin natsuwa ɗaya daga al'adu na Islama.",

  "promptWisdomOfJesus": "Rubuta gajeriyar hikima daga Annabai kamar aka koya a Islama. Ɗauki daga Qur'ani ko Hadisi da saurin bayani kamar ʻulamain Islama suka fahimta. Canja jaya-jaya: kirki, haƙuri, fahimi, imani, ko aiki na yau-yau. Samu ayar Qur'ani ko Hadisir musamman da aikin aiki ɗaya.",

  "promptHumilityCharacter": "Rubuta tunani kan fahimi (Tawadhu) da kirki (Akhlaq). Ɗauki daga koyarwar Qur'ani, misalin Annabi Muhammad, da al'adu girke da kirki a Islama. Canja jaya-jaya: fahimi a mulkin karfi, gane kusurun, kula da juna, ko girke mai zafi a tunani. Samu ayar Qur'ani guda da aikin aiki ɗaya don yi.",

  "promptOvercomingTemptation": "Rubuta tunani kan illi jajire da tsaya a hanyar daidai. Ɗauki daga jagoran Qur'ani, alkhamar Allah (Dhikr), sallah (Salah), da misalan masu imani da suka ɗiba wahalar. Canja hanya kowane lokaci. Samu ayar Qur'ani guda da dabarun aiki ɗaya don salo da 24 awake.",

  "promptEveningReflection": "Rubuta tunani mai natsuwa kan jiya tushe a al'adu alkhamar jiya (Adhkar al-Masaa'). Karfafa godiya, tunani kan kanka (Muhasabah), da tabbatarwa ga Allah kafin baje. Samu tambayoyi 3–5 na tunani game da ranar, addu'a ɗam-ɗam ta kammala, da ayar Qur'ani guda.",

