  "dailyScripture9Ref": "Qur'ani 57:4",
  "dailyScripture10Text": "Allah ba ya haɗa jiya bauri wanda ba ta karɓa ba.",
  "dailyScripture10Ref": "Qur'ani 2:286",
  "dailyScripture11Text": "Wa kuwan tabbatarwa ga Allah — Allah isa mawallansa.",
  "dailyScripture11Ref": "Qur'ani 65:3",
  "dailyScripture12Text": "Jinni na taɓi dukkan abubuwan.",
  "dailyScripture12Ref": "Qur'ani 7:156",
  "dailyScripture13Text": "Sa'ad da jiyata suka tambayi ka game da ni — ni ne kusa. Na amsa mai addu'a sa idan ya karanta mini.",
  "dailyScripture13Ref": "Qur'ani 2:186",
  "dailyScripture14Text": "Wa kuwan yi aiki da muwa a rai, namiji ko mache — mun yi masu raina mai kyau.",
  "dailyScripture14Ref": "Qur'ani 16:97",
  "dailyScripture15Text": "Tabbas Allah ba shi canja ra'ayin kasa sai kazo sun canja ra'ayin kansu.",
  "dailyScripture15Ref": "Qur'ani 13:11",
  "dailyScripture16Text": "Saboda haka ji rauni ka ba shiru, da kuma kuma za ku karɓi iko idan ku mai sa aiki.",
  "dailyScripture16Ref": "Qur'ani 3:139",
  "dailyScripture17Text": "Jiyannina wajen tabu suka damje kansu, kada kunan yanzu a jinni Allah. Tabbas Allah yana gafara dukkan zunuba.",
  "dailyScripture17Ref": "Qur'ani 39:53",
  "dailyScripture18Text": "Wa kuwan tsoron Allah — shi zai yi wa hanya ta gida, kuma ya ba shi ta inda ba ya buƙe.",
  "dailyScripture18Ref": "Qur'ani 65:2-3",
  "dailyScripture19Text": "Kada kunan yanzu a jinni Allah.",
  "dailyScripture19Ref": "Qur'ani 12:87",
  "dailyScripture20Text": "Da mun daidaita Qur'ani don karatawar. Saboda haka akwai wa zai ƙaddamawa da zikiru?",
  "dailyScripture20Ref": "Qur'ani 54:17",
  "dailyScripture21Text": "Ya fito ka saka da kuma ya ba ka jagoron.",
  "dailyScripture21Ref": "Qur'ani 93:7",
  "dailyScripture22Text": "Wa ubankun yace: Ku karanta mini; Zan amsa ku.",
  "dailyScripture22Ref": "Qur'ani 40:60",
  "dailyScripture23Text": "Da mun karamnta jiyar Adam.",
  "dailyScripture23Ref": "Qur'ani 17:70",
  "dailyScripture24Text": "Ku nemi taimako da haƙuri da sallah.",
  "dailyScripture24Ref": "Qur'ani 2:45",
  "dailyScripture25Text": "Wa kuwan yi aiki dalilin zarra ya gani shi.",
  "dailyScripture25Ref": "Qur'ani 99:7",
  "dailyScripture26Text": "Ba shakka taimako Allah shi ne kusa.",
  "dailyScripture26Ref": "Qur'ani 2:214",
  "dailyScripture27Text": "Wa kuwan godiya — godiyarsa shine fa'ida ga kansa.",
  "dailyScripture27Ref": "Qur'ani 31:12",

  "dailyReflection0": "Yayin da ranar ta kllosa, yi tunani akan lokaci inda jinni Allah ya bayyana.",
  "dailyReflection1": "Kawo da abubuwan da suka nauya zuciyanka a ranar.",
  "dailyReflection2": "Gani baiyar daya daga ranar da suka yi godiya ga Allah.",
  "dailyReflection3": "Yi hutawa da sani cewa ka kunshe a jinni Allah.",
  "dailyReflection4": "Yi tunani akan inda an kira ka don nuna jinni da tausayi.",
  "dailyReflection5": "Bari abubuwan da ba ka iya canja da tabbatar ga shirin Allah.",
  "dailyReflection6": "Yayin da ranar ta kammala, samu lafiya a alkhamar Allah.",
  "dailyReflection7": "Yi tunani kamar yadda ka onora sallahi a ranar, ka godiya ga Allah.",
  "dailyReflection8": "Yi tunani akan lokaci inda haƙuri ya jagoce aiki a ranar.",
  "dailyReflection9": "Nemi gafara akan dukkan kusurun — jinni Allah ba shi ido.",
  "dailyReflection10": "Gani mutu ɗaya da ka nuna jinni a ranar, ka yi addu'a.",
  "dailyReflection11": "Yi hutawa da godiya: me Allah ya ba ka a ranar ba za ka buƙe?",
  "dailyReflection12": "Yi tunani akan ayar Qur'ani da ta takaitawa a inda ka jiya.",
  "dailyReflection13": "Yi tunani kamar yadda ka amfani da jiya — ba da gida ga Allah.",
  "dailyReflection14": "Yi hutawa da sani cewa dukkan wahalii na ranar, Allah ya tare da ka.",
  "dailyReflection15": "Yi tunani akan hanya ɗaya da ka hidima iyali ko gida.",
  "dailyReflection16": "Yayin da dare ya farcewa, yi Tawbah — Allah ya so masu tawbah.",
  "dailyReflection17": "Yi tunani akan kyau Allah ya saka a ranar, ko ita banuwa.",
  "dailyReflection18": "Yi tunani akan abin da ka sani a ranar da yadda ya kusan ka ga Allah.",
  "dailyReflection19": "Bari abubuwan da suka damje ka a gida ga Allah — shi ya ɗauke abubuwan.",
  "dailyReflection20": "Yi tunani akan lokaci da ka iya zaɓe kyau, da aka sani.",
  "dailyReflection21": "Yi addu'a wa waɗanda suke cikin wahalii — addu'ar ka shine kaɗa.",
  "dailyReflection22": "Tunantana baiyar da ka mara ganinki da godiya ga Allah.",
  "dailyReflection23": "Yi tunani kan niyya a ranar — ko ta kasua ta Allah? Gida ta farƙa.",
  "dailyReflection24": "Yayin da dare ya shiru, sauraro jinni Allah.",
  "dailyReflection25": "Yi tunani kan inda ka sami karfi a ranar — karfi daga Allah.",
  "dailyReflection26": "Gani wani abin da za ka yi gida, saboda Allah, da ba ka yi jiya.",
  "dailyReflection27": "Yayin da ka shiryo don baje, ba da jiya ga Allah — shi ne mafi kyau na mai alubakin.",

